name: AnnoyingSounds
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: annoying sounds
des:
Are you tired of your annoying roommate, annoy him with the mosquito. Test out your new sub woofer with Extreme bass! Or just have some fun with annoying sounds!

Annoying sounds has the list of sounds:
Air horn
Alarm
Bass Extreme
Bass Light
Creepy
Dial up
Mosquito
Nails on board
Vuvuzela
And random 

With more sounds to come!
Just say Alexa start annoying sounds, then say random or pick a sound from the list!

***Warning may be loud!!!***
Say "Alexa stop" to quit out of the current sound.

Bug fixes and recommendations to new sounds are welcomed.

Thank you for trying.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
